{"tid":749483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基奧特：有人常用世界盃冠軍寸我 如今輪到我了...","createTime":"2018-07-20T05:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T13:45:37.000Z","uid":147522,"like":203,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"dfca9a667adcf3de7094071b12e8d0eeddec922e","tid":749483,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"　　作為法國隊的主力中鋒，基奧特剛剛跟隨球隊拿到了世界盃冠軍。這令大基奧特身心愉悅。他談到了之前阿仙奴隊友奧斯爾總在他面前誇耀自己是世界冠軍的往事。<br />\n<br />\n　　如今效力車路士的基奧特說：「我在阿仙奴時與德國球員關係非常不錯，之前我真的非常羨慕他們。有時候，當奧斯爾在訓練當中輸了之後，他總是一副不可一世的樣子說&lsquo;嘿，別說了，我可是世界冠軍啊。&rsquo;我也想不出什麼話來回擊他，畢竟這是事實啊。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「現在我也終於體會到這種感覺，真的太美妙了。而且不會再有人跟我這麼說了，這種感覺很不錯。」"},{"pid":"30e7ee18582775e0b57e4f442bc23bb86692b1b7","tid":749483,"uid":120715,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"做咩暗串美斯"},{"pid":"a860ec8f2bd231928b2474a7d35d61b456e7fc53","tid":749483,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":48,"score":-42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:31:56.000Z","msg":"銀河唯一射唔入，世界盃人物"},{"pid":"1a0825998b4c6b18e0022e0b9da8779ab4142126","tid":749483,"uid":63588,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:35:06.000Z","msg":"中文幾好"},{"pid":"fd6e4e3604f44f5fae3ca040ac59f4e5d6c5778e","tid":749483,"uid":10819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"睇完第一段以為係往死裡打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a32f1d0e7c41f8c0a054869dd8896160a4c8c9","tid":749483,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"豬蛇d霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65af3f5eaa9e2a4f833c806eda996c7c07dc4d5f","tid":749483,"uid":33864,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"可惜&hellip; 佢已經冇機會串返奧燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7141bb5bfae33ed3a58408363334777ef0be638","tid":749483,"uid